cfv 1.5.1  Copyright 2000 Matt Mueller <donut@azstarnet.com>

Install:
1) make sure you have python installed 
1.5) make sure the python-zlib module and/or the python-fchksum
module is installed.  (Preferably, fchksum, as it is faster.
http://www.azstarnet.com/~donut/programs/fchksum.html)
2) run make with no arguments to see possible installation methods
3) run your chosen method (or manually put cfv and cfv.1 where you want)
4) read man page, cfv -h, etc.  have fun.


